為達到示威目的而合理地需要使用的最低程度武力。示威者在達到目的後，會停止使用武力。示威者在制訂使用武力指引的時候，有參考外國示威的做法及考慮不同情境的獨特情況。"},{"pid":"9fe3d6e06366553849cfb7f236aff24405a05d86","tid":1497046,"uid":113007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T00:18:33.000Z","msg":"承認同割席係兩回事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />核爆都唔撚割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3ce1d9ff6ba4e83dfcfcad8654aac51f467c311","tid":1497046,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T00:19:14.000Z","msg":"又係BBC"},{"pid":"8593f435ce6d2d74a9f41c5c92f84a9153daa85d","tid":1497046,"uid":295572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffe1878362c355016f09ec86daaf312fb4bbb6d9","tid":1497046,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T19:27:35.000Z","msg":"&quot;People are fighting for what they want, <br />\nthe truth is some of them might be a little bit violent during the protest..&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去聽16:40<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/sounds/play/p07lbr20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fsounds%2Fplay%2Fp07lbr20&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1T1D2OVAb2WcgpQnG2a6kfc%3D&h=9bee1fc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.co.uk/sounds/play/p07lbr20</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:04:21.000Z","msg":"巴打幫推<br />\n［突發］ 人鏈用個tag #handsacrossHK<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1498571\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1498571</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3c1c996b1174a3e9d77cb147dd967629e25269c9","tid":1497046,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:07:45.000Z","msg":"武力英文係咩先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla